{"tid":798756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺暴雨百萬Type R被浸　網民食花生：直版任驗","createTime":"2018-08-29T13:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T13:51:20.000Z","uid":203619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e499d515664c9c064a9085b11066552eb93f5ca8","tid":798756,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fbkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001.html&d=yzEk5Ertmxc4OcHYQPlnnmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=1dcf13a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/photo/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180829204733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180829204733&h=37c283c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港各區暴雨不斷，新界多個地區都出現水浸，不少靚車突然變成「水浸車」！有網民在粉嶺布格仔拍下照片，有多架本田Type R跑車被浸，當中包括一眾車迷趨之若鶩的新款Civic Type R。這架馬力達320匹的新一代辣跑於去年推出，新車價接近港幣60萬，更是限量發售。<br />\n<br />\n但對於今次「水浸辣車」網民普遍「食花生」行先。有人就留言，「邊個話得日本有水浸車」。亦有人冷言一句，「直版任驗無大撞」，幸災樂禍車主日後可將車輛以「無撞過、任檢驗」作賣點在二手市場出售。<br />\n<br />\n除了型號較新的Civic Type R，被洪水淹浸的還有一架車齡估計達20年的本田S-2000開蓬跑車。近年香港出現了購買這類八、九十年代日本車熱潮。這些被稱為「中古車」的二手車有價有市，一輛車齡20年的「一代戰車」叫價可高達港幣20至30萬。以被浸的S-2000為例，1999年出廠的同款車二手價格可超過港幣20萬。換句話說，照片中所拍下的多架水浸車，總價值已超過港幣100萬。<br />\n<br />\n「中古車」縱然保值力強，但今次仍難保「乾爽」。有網民就留言表示心痛，不過也有網民戲言，建議車主用巨型膠袋包起座駕，就不用再怕暴雨水浸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/photo/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180829204733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180829204733&h=6fdc2aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一輛新款Type R幾乎被浸過車輪。(Facebook專頁「open car」圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/photo/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180829204733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180829204733&h=eef94fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一輛被浸的火紅色Civic Type R。(Facebook專頁「open car」圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/photo/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_04p.jpg?20180829204733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20180829204733&h=dfe178bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有車齡較高的S-2000被浸。(Facebook專頁「open car」圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/photo/bkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_06p.jpg?20180829204733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180829191836329-0829_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20180829204733&h=06dab4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民戲言，車主可用巨型膠袋以避免車輛被浸。"},{"pid":"91994b8e8f6350d513dccfcadd580e03393e657d","tid":798756,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"用condom笠住架車咪得囉"},{"pid":"172b445315f0b8b4d2d212d36ffeb8eea24b6f87","tid":798756,"uid":203619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"到底點用膠袋粒到架車咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}